Beach facing Luxurious comfort
Beautiful location overlooking the beach and very big rooms with a great view of the sea . There are a lot of restaurants at a walking distance from the hotel.There is a convenience store just next door .The Staff is helpful although not everyone understands English.The buffet spread is very good and has a good choice for vegetarians also There was one problem although the hotel was not responsible for it At 5 30-6 am on both days of our stay there was a program on the beach and the loud speaker made it difficult to sleep Other than that it was a delightful experience
