Himadri & Akshat wrote a review Feb 2020
Noida, India9 contributions1 helpful vote
Superb!
We stayed here for 5 nights which included the lunar new year 2020. We were in a 2 bedroom appt and it was such a fantastic experience. We had two balconies that overlooked sea. Every morning we used to wake up with the sunrise and look at the beautiful sea. Breakfast is worth having. They serve international as well as vietnamese foods. We loved trying new things there with a variety of fruits. The infinity pool at roof top was fantastic. In evenings it used to get windy and chilly because of 23rd floor but morning and afternoons were fabulous. They serve pizza, burgers, cocktails near pool. And oh their coconut coffee is a must try ‚ù§ We tried their pho and fried rice as dinner with sauteed vegetables. It was good. I wish they had more options in dinner though. The spa at‚Ä¶
